message: |

    hygen {bold lib new} --name {bold NAME} {italic [--stateful]} {italic [--functional]}

    Generates a lib and a test.

       NAME           The lib name in kebab-case ({bold required}).
       --stateful     Generate a stateful lib (optional).
       --functional   Generate a functional lib (optional).

    If no flags given, will generate a Purelib.

